{
  "id": "coco",
  "title": "Coco",
  "year": 2017,
  "characters": [
    "ABUELITA ELENA",
    "ALL",
    "DANTE",
    "DE LA CRUZ",
    "INTERVIEWER",
    "MAMA",
    "MAMA COCO",
    "MARIACHI",
    "MIGUEL",
    "NEIGHBOR",
    "NUN",
    "PADRE",
    "PAPA",
    "SHOE SHINER",
    "TIO BERTO",
    "TOUR GUIDE"
  ],
  "lines": [
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Sometimes, I think I\u2019m cursed."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Because of something that happened before I was even born."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "See, a long time ago, there was this family."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "The papa, he was a musician."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "He and his family would sing and dance and count their blessings."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "But he also had a dream."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "To play for the world."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "And one day, he left with his guitar and never returned."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "And the mama\u2026"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "She didn\u2019t have time to cry over that walkaway musician."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "After banishing all music from her life she found a way\u2026"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "to provide for her daughter."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "She rolled up her sleeves and she learned to make shoes."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "She could have made candy, or fireworks, or sparkly underwear\u2026 for wrestlers, but no, she chose shoes."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Then she taught her daughter to make shoes."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "And later, she taught her son-in-law."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Then her grandkids got roped in."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "As her family grew, so did the business."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Music had torn her family apart."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "But shoes held them all together."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "You see, that woman was my great-great-grandmother, Mama Imelda."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "She died way before I was born."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "But my family still tells her story every year on Dia de los Muertos\u2026 the Day of the Dead."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "And her little girl, she\u2019s my great-grandmother, Mama Coco."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Hola, Mama Coco."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA COCO",
      "text": "How are you, Julio?"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Actually, my name is Miguel."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Mama Coco has trouble remembering things."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "But it\u2019s good to talk to her anyway."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "So, I tell her pretty much everything."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I used to run like this."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "But now I run like this which is way faster."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "And the winner is Luchadora Coco!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I have a dimple on this side, but not on this side."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Dimple, no dimple."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Dimple, no dimple."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Miguel, eat your food."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "My abuelita, she\u2019s Mama Coco\u2019s daughter."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Oh, you\u2019re a twig, mijo."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Have some more."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "No, gracias."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "I asked if you would like more tamales!"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Si?"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "That\u2019s what I thought you said!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Abuelita runs our house just like Mama Imelda did."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "No music!"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "No music!"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "No music!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I think we\u2019re the only family in Mexico who hates music."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "And my family\u2019s fine with that. But me\u2026"
    },
    {
      "character": "PAPA",
      "text": "Be back by lunch, mijo."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "Love you, Mama."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I am not like the rest of my family!"
    },
    {
      "character": "NEIGHBOR",
      "text": "Hola, Miguel!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Hola!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MARIACHI",
      "text": "Muchas gracias."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "De nada, Miguel."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Hey! Dante!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Sit. Down."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Roll over. Shake."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Fist bump!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Good boy, Dante!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I know I\u2019m not supposed to love music."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "But it\u2019s not my fault!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "It\u2019s his!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Ernesto de la Cruz."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "The greatest musician of all time."
    },
    {
      "character": "TOUR GUIDE",
      "text": "Right here in this very plaza, Ernesto de la Cruz took his first steps\u2026 toward becoming the most beloved singer in Mexican history."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "He started out a total nobody from Santa Cecilia, like me."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "But when he played music, he made people fall in love with him."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "He starred in movies."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "He had the coolest guitar!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "He could fly!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "And he wrote the best songs."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "But my all-time favorite, it\u2019s\u2026"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "He lived the kind of life you dream about."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Until 1942."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "When he was crushed by a giant bell."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I want to be just like him."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Sometimes, I look at de la Cruz and I get this feeling like we\u2019re connected."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Like if he could play music, maybe someday, I could too."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "If it wasn\u2019t for my family."
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "Aya-yay, muchacho."
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "Huh?"
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "I asked for a shoe shine not your life story."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Oh, yeah. Sorry."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I just can\u2019t really talk about any of this at home. So\u2026"
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "If I were you, I\u2019d march right up to my family and say\u2026"
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "\u201cHey, I\u2019m a musician. Deal with it.\u201d"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I could never say that."
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "You are a musician, no?"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I don\u2019t know."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I mean, I only really play for myself."
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "Ah! Did de la Cruz become the world\u2019s best musician by hiding his skills?"
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "No! He walked out onto that plaza and he played out loud."
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "Mira, mira, they\u2019re setting up for tonight!"
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "The music competition for Dia de Muertos."
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "You want to be like your hero?"
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "You should sign up!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Uh-uh."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "My family would freak!"
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "Look, if you\u2019re too scared then, well, have fun making shoes."
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "Come on, what did de la Cruz always say?"
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "Seize your moment?"
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "Show me what you got, muchacho."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "ABUELITA ELENA: Miguel!"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Abuelita!"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "What are you doing here?"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "You leave my grandson alone."
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "Dona, please!"
    },
    {
      "character": "SHOE SHINER",
      "text": "I was just getting a shine."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "I know your tricks, mariachi."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "What did he say to you?"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "He was just showing me his guitar."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Shame on you."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "My grandson is a sweet little angelito querido cielito."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "He wants no part of your music, mariachi."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "You keep away from him."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Ay, pobrecito."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Oh, estas bien, mijo."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "You know better than to be here in this place!"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "You will come home. Now."
    },
    {
      "character": "TIO BERTO",
      "text": "How many times have we told you?"
    },
    {
      "character": "TIO BERTO",
      "text": "That plaza is crawling with mariachis."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Yes, Tio Berto."
    },
    {
      "character": "TIO BERTO",
      "text": "Never name a street dog."
    },
    {
      "character": "TIO BERTO",
      "text": "They\u2019ll follow you forever."
    },
    {
      "character": "TIO BERTO",
      "text": "Now, go get my shoe."
    },
    {
      "character": "PAPA",
      "text": "I found your son in Mariachi Plaza."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "Ay, Miguel!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "You know how Abuelita feels about the plaza."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I was just shining shoes."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "A musician\u2019s shoes!"
    },
    {
      "character": "PAPA",
      "text": "But the plaza\u2019s where all the foot traffic is."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "If Abuelita says no more plaza, then no more plaza."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "But what about tonight?"
    },
    {
      "character": "PAPA",
      "text": "What\u2019s tonight?"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Well, they\u2019re having this talent show."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "And I thought I might\u2026"
    },
    {
      "character": "PAPA",
      "text": "Sign up?"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Well, maybe?"
    },
    {
      "character": "TIO BERTO",
      "text": "You have to have talent to be in a talent show."
    },
    {
      "character": "TIO BERTO",
      "text": "What are you gonna do?"
    },
    {
      "character": "TIO BERTO",
      "text": "Shine shoes?"
    },
    {
      "character": "PAPA",
      "text": "It\u2019s Dia de los Muertos."
    },
    {
      "character": "PAPA",
      "text": "No one\u2019s going anywhere."
    },
    {
      "character": "PAPA",
      "text": "Tonight is about family."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Ofrenda room."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Vamonos."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "Don\u2019t give me that look."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "Dia de los Muertos is the one night of the year our ancestors can come visit us."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "We\u2019ve put their photos on the ofrenda so their spirits can cross over."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "That is very important."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "If we don\u2019t put them up, they can\u2019t come."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "We made all this food, set out the things they loved in life, mijo."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "All this work to bring the family together."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "I don\u2019t want you sneaking off to who knows where."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "Where are you going?"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I thought we were done."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Ay, Dios mio."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Being part of this family means being here for this family."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "I don\u2019t want to see you end up like\u2026"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Like Mama Coco\u2019s papa?"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Never mention that man!"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "He\u2019s better off forgotten."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "But you\u2019re the one who\u2026"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "I was just\u2026"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "But\u2026 I\u2026"
    },
    {
      "character": "PAPA",
      "text": "Papa? Papa is home?"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Mama, calmese, calmese."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA COCO",
      "text": "Papa is coming home?"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "No, Mama."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "It\u2019s okay. I\u2019m here."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA COCO",
      "text": "Who are you?"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Rest, Mama."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "I\u2019m hard on you because I care, Miguel."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Miguel? Miguel?"
    },
    {
      "character": "PAPA",
      "text": "What are we going to do with that boy?"
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "You\u2019re right."
    },
    {
      "character": "MAMA",
      "text": "That\u2019s just what he needs."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Someone could hear me."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I wish someone wanted to hear me."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Other than you. Ew. Okay."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Perfecto!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I have to sing."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I have to play!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "The music, it\u2019s not just in me, it is me."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "When life gets me down, I play my guitar."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "The rest of the world may follow the rules, but I must follow my heart."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "Ugh!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "You know that feeling like there\u2019s a song in the air and\u2026 it\u2019s playing just for you?"
    },
    {
      "character": "PADRE",
      "text": "You must have faith, sister."
    },
    {
      "character": "NUN",
      "text": "Oh, but, Padre, he will never listen."
    },
    {
      "character": "DE LA CRUZ",
      "text": "He will listen. To music."
    },
    {
      "character": "DE LA CRUZ",
      "text": "Never underestimate the power of music."
    },
    {
      "character": "NUN",
      "text": "But my father, he will never give his permission."
    },
    {
      "character": "DE LA CRUZ",
      "text": "I am done asking permission."
    },
    {
      "character": "DE LA CRUZ",
      "text": "When you see your moment, you mustn\u2019t let it pass you by."
    },
    {
      "character": "DE LA CRUZ",
      "text": "You must seize it!"
    },
    {
      "character": "INTERVIEWER",
      "text": "Senor de la Cruz, what did it take for you to seize your moment?"
    },
    {
      "character": "DE LA CRUZ",
      "text": "I had to have faith in my dream."
    },
    {
      "character": "DE LA CRUZ",
      "text": "No one was going to hand it to me."
    },
    {
      "character": "DE LA CRUZ",
      "text": "It was up to me to reach for that dream."
    },
    {
      "character": "DE LA CRUZ",
      "text": "Grab it tight and make it come true."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "\u2026and make it come true."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "No more hiding, Dante."
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I got to seize my moment!"
    },
    {
      "character": "MIGUEL",
      "text": "I\u2019m gonna play in Mariachi Plaza if it kills me."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "Dia de los Muertos has begun!"
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "No, no. We have to make a clear path."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "The petals guide our ancestors home."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "We don\u2019t want their spirits to get lost."
    },
    {
      "character": "ABUELITA ELENA",
      "text": "We want them to come and enjoy all the food and drinks on the ofrenda."
    },
    {
      "character": "PAPA",
      "text": "Mama!"
    },
    {
